chunks.html_content: Call the National Benefit Fraud Hotline to report benefit fraud to the Department for Work and Pensions (DWP).
chunks.plain_content:
National Benefit Fraud Hotline
Call the National Benefit Fraud Hotline to report benefit fraud to the Department for Work and Pensions (DWP).

chunks.html_content: You can also report suspected benefit fraud online or by post.
chunks.plain_content:
National Benefit Fraud Hotline
You can also report suspected benefit fraud online or by post.

National Benefit Fraud Hotline
This guide is also available in Welsh (Cymraeg).

chunks.html_content:
National Benefit Fraud Hotline
Telephone: 0800 854 440
Welsh language: 0800 678 3722
Textphone: 0800 328 0512
British Sign Language (BSL) video relay service if you’re on a computer - find out how to use the service on mobile or tablet

Monday to Friday, 8am to 6pm
Find out about call charges
